The paper deals with Stackelberg security games, which are a subfield of game theory (cs.GT) applied to security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses learning approaches for optimizing the defender's expected utility, which falls under machine learning (cs.AI) and decision making (cs.LG). Finally, the paper mentions green security, which is a subfield of sustainable computing (cs.SI).
